{"word":"φόως","slug":"φόως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φόως</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>epic <a href='S:lengthened'>lengthd.</a> from <el>φῶς</el>, which is itself <a href='S:contracted, contraction'>contr.</a> from <a href='S:φάος'><el>φάος</el></a>\n<p/><i>light</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, only in <a href='S:nominative'>nom.</a> and <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> sg.;<p/>"}]}